ps%2C158&sr=8-6\",\"imageUrl\":\"/images/products/Sweetie-Siamese-Cat.png\",\"flags\":{\"gifts\":true,\"topPick\":false,\"camera\":false,\"internetAccess\":false,\"affiliateAgreement\":false}},\"$5:props:children:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:props:items:10\",\"$5:props:children:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:props:items:11\"],\"title\":\"Kids & Family picks at a glance\",\"text\":\"Quickly scan type, audience, highlight, rating, and price.\"}]\n9:[\"$\",\"$L21\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$22\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@23\"}]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-3xl space-y-5 text-base leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-lg sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"0\",{\"children\":[\"Research has shown that interactive pets can improve the lives of children by supporting interactive learning, personalized engagement, empathy, and technology skills. (\",[\"$\",\"$L24\",null,{\"href\":\"/kids-research\",\"className\":\"underline text-trust-700 hover:text-trust-900\",\"children\":\"See a list of articles\"}],\".)\"]}],[\"$\",\"div\",\"1\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"className\":\"text-slate-900\",\"children\":\"Why do families choose interactive pets?\"}],\" \",\"For many families, an interactive pet is the bridge between “wanting a pet” and “being ready for one.” The research on children and AI companions suggests they can support empathy, nurturing behavior, and basic technology fluency — especially with models that respond when cared for. Parents also gravitate toward this category for practical reasons: no shedding, no allergies, no training, and no veterinary bills. Younger children get a companion they can talk to and look after; older children with an interest in technology get an introduction to robotics that’s more engaging than a static toy.\"]}]]}]\nc:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 max-w-3xl rounded-3xl border border-trust-200 bg-trust-50 p-6 sm:p-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-trust-900 sm:text-2xl\",\"children\":\"What to look for when choosing for kids or families\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Age appropriateness\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Age appropriateness\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Some models are sturdy enough for toddlers; others have small parts or fragile mechanisms better suited to older children.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Durability\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Durability\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Look for washable fabrics, replaceable batteries, and warranties that cover normal wear and tear.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Educational depth\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Educational depth\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Some interactive pets include programmable behavior or coding features that scale with the child's curiosity over time.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Screen-free vs. app-required\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Screen-free vs. app-required\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"Many parents prefer screen-free models for younger children; older kids may enjoy companion apps that extend play.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Voice and conversation\",{\"className\":\"text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700 sm:text-base sm:leading-8\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-slate-900\",\"children\":[\"Voice and conversation\",\".\"]}],\" \",\"A